# Cargo
Cargo.lock
# Remove Cargo.lock from gitignore if creating an executable, leave it for libraries
# More info here https://doc.rust-lang.org/cargo/guide/cargo-toml.html#cargolock
# Cargo.lock is ignored for binary projects.

# Rust backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

